casebody.data:
Virginia JAMES, appellant,
v.
FEDERAL ELECTIONS COMMISSION. No. 12-683. Supreme Court of the United States April 7, 2014.

Case below, 914 F.Supp.2d 1.

Appeal from the United States District Court for the District of Columbia. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States District Court for the District of Columbia for further consideration in light of McCutcheon v. Federal Election Comm'n, 572 U.S. ---- (2014).
